
------
Usage
------

1. 'make' generates a library named 'libsortgpu.so'
2. include 'sort_gpu.hpp' and link the library via '-L/path/ -lsortgpu'
3. see sort.cu for examples. In particular, call 'sortGPU::init_xxx()' before using 'sortGPU::sort_matrix_rows_xxx()', and call 'sortGPU::final_xxx()' afterwards


------
Files
------

sort.cu
  an example of benchmarking different sorts (Thrust, CUB and Modern GPU)

sort_gpu.hpp
  header file to be included for the sorts

kernel_thrust.cu, kernel_cub.cu, kernel_mgpu.cu
  implementation of sorting using different libraries

timer_gpu.cu, timer_gpu.hpp
  utility for GPU timing

